cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.DM, cs.DB, cs.CG. 

The paper deals with the problem of indexing a weighted sequence to efficiently answer pattern matching queries. This problem is related to data structures (cs.DS), algorithms and complexity (cs.CC), and databases (cs.DB). The paper also involves combinatorics (cs.DM) and computational geometry (cs.CG) in the construction of the data structure.
